Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:15.05,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\blur1\pos(453.949,588.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:15.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:19.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:23.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:26.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:30.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:33.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:36.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:40.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:44.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:48.40,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:51.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:54.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:00:59.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:02.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.37,0:01:11.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:14.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:16.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:19.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.46,0:01:29.81,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,I need to get myself together by the\NAll-Japan Motocross Championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That wretched Hongo...\Nwe'll show him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You are our most talented\Ncombatants, re-modified and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:02:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,brainwashed for our\Nthird attack operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The cyborgs shown here have successively\Nbeen defeated by the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.68,0:02:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We've run their data through\Nour Shocker computers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.33,0:02:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and created a new one by combining\Nall of their strengths: Gebacondor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.44,0:02:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But Gebacondor is\Nnot yet awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Gebacondor requires the\Nblood of young women to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:36.37,Static Texts,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HFCFFFE&\b1\pos(475.81,170.405)}Blood-Sucking Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:36.37,Static Texts,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HFCFFFE&\b1\pos(510,670.5)}Gebacondor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's a bit sudden, but we'd\Nlike to get married at this church.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you accommodate us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.62,0:03:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I take you to be my spouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.47,0:03:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,in richness and in poorness,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in sickness and in health,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,until death do us part.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.27,0:04:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought fresh blood\Nfrom that young woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink deep, and become a\Nloyal soldier of Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Gebacondor... rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Disrupt humanity's\Npeaceful lives
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and do all in your power to\Nhelp Shocker conquer the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, go and test your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise, Gebacondor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That foolish Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead for sure, this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"To my dear comrades at Snack Amigo.\NTaki Kazuya."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... wasn't he the winner of last\Nyear's All-Japan Motocross Championships?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi's perpetual rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.78,0:06:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be confident, getting married\Nwith the championships on the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Whereas Takeshi's out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me...\NI haven't seen Takeshi for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.71,0:06:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what he's up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Some kind of important\Nresearch, I think he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to dedicate all his time to\Ndriving in the run-up to the championships,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but his research is\Nimportant, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess living a\Ndouble life isn't easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:17.61,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\3c&H3D6668&\c&HBEEBE7&\bord4.5}Jonan University\NBiochemistry Laboratory
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to\Nyour friend's wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure he\Nsaid he was coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It is strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He said on the phone\Nthat he'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You want that woman's\Nblood, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There are too many\Npeople in attendance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck at the\NChampionships, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll get an interesting honeymoon\Nfrom her new racer husband, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess Takeshi\Ndidn't make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoko? Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:33.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When wind spins the turbine in\Ncyborg Hongo Takeshi's belt,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:35.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he transforms into\Nthe Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's your chance!\NTake the girl and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:29.85,Bumper Episode 2-13,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\pos(355,520)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor Yoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think she'll\Never recover?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn that Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What an inhuman act...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a wonder\Nthings didn't get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd given up,\Nassuming it was hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when the Kamen\NRider rode in and saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:09.80,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\an7\3c&H1B2B8B&}Phone
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what Takeshi is up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to head out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you getting married\Ntoo, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You really shouldn't do it\Nhere, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Mr. Tachibana...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.11,0:15:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been scoping\Nout this church.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Something seems off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to avenge Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,When I look at her in that\Ncondition, I get so angry,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.93,0:15:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need to take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,After what that boy said, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's definitely something strange\Nabout it, but we still can't prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When we went, there was just that\None old woman playing the organ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The creepy one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.94,0:15:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's a Shocker\Nbase under that church,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:15:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and that woman is\Nstanding guard there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I did think there was something\Nfishy about that priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't spot anything that seemed\Nlike it could lead underground...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the old woman being there\Nmade it was hard to look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to make Shocker pay\Nfor what they did to Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, hang on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.95,0:16:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Could what be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I have a perfect plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Investigate as thoroughly as\Nyou can during the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.25,0:16:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.13,0:16:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If things get\Ndangerous, make tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:16:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you, Jiro, take Kazuko to\Nbe your lawfully wedded wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go taking this\Nseriously, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you, Kazuko, take Jiro to be\Nyour lawfully wedded husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.19,0:17:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to go faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When did he get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll finish you this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.63,0:21:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider can't beat him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.37,0:21:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll going run out of\Npower at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.39,0:21:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!\NUse the Cyclone to get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you running away? Coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.26,0:22:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.87,0:23:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.38,0:23:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get back, too!\NWait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.06,0:23:18.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The danger had\Npassed once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.24,0:23:24.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider's heroics had protected\Nanother precious young life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.61,0:23:28.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But as long as Shocker was out\Nthere, modifying
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.29,0:23:30.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,humans and plotting\Nto conquer the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:35.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi's—the Kamen\NRider's battle would never end!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.99,0:23:40.59,Cont,,510,0,170,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.90,0:23:43.04,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,486.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.57,0:23:45.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.85,0:23:46.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is Yamogerus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.13,0:23:46.84,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HFCFFFE&\b1\pos(490.495,301.833)}The Murderous Yamogerus
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.98,0:23:50.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker steals the Danger Light\Njust developed by Doctor Shirakawa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.95,0:23:53.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and uses it to engineer\Nhumanity's extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.61,0:23:56.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.49,0:23:59.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "The Murderous Yamogerus."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:10.84,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.43,0:24:13.43,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.43,0:24:15.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.39,0:24:18.43,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.93,0:24:20.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.81,0:24:22.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.69,0:24:24.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.48,0:24:25.82,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.27,0:24:28.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.36,0:24:33.83,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.03,0:24:37.62,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.62,0:24:41.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.71,0:24:45.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:36.37,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HFCFFFE&\b1\pos(480.495,216.833)}Blood-Sucking Monster Gebacondor